{"data":[{"date":"15:04 03/08","title":"Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/9/liverpool-giam-gia-ban-origi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong ngo\u00e0i Roberto Firmino l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Sturridge, Danny Ings v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/9/liverpool-giam-gia-ban-origi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Wolfsburg theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 6 b\u00e0n sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOrigi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Liverpool, Origi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Origi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Divock Origi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"origi\" title=\"origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/30/origi-toi-khong-nghi-liverpool-lai-thua-theo-cach-nhu-vay.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Origi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00f2i 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 cao. Theo The Mirror, Liverpool v\u1eeba gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Origi xu\u1ed1ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nhanh ch\u00f3ng thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Hi\u1ec7n Watford \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Watford ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00f3 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995. Ngo\u00e0i Watford th\u00ec Besiktas v\u00e0 Fenerbahce c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1956","checkdouble":"193640"},{"date":"15:21 03/08","title":"Toby Alderweireld l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/toby-alderweireld-len-tieng-ve-tin-don-chuyen-toi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Toby Alderweireld ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld. Mourinho \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"trung ve Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/toby-alderweireld-len-tieng-ve-tin-don-chuyen-toi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Davinson Sanchez. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 M.U chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989. M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Toby Alderweireld, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Tottenham \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00ednh m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Toby Alderweireld ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"Chelsea mua Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/mu-muon-mua-alderweireld-mua-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Toby Alderweireld kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Tottenham, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alderweireld, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina-172-192619.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U s\u1ebd mua Yerry Mina </span>c\u1ee7a Barca ho\u1eb7c Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester. Theo Daily Mail v\u00e0 ESPN, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1955","checkdouble":"193641"},{"date":"15:02 03/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u0169 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Palestine?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-se-trung-thanh-voi-chien-thuat-cu-o-tran-viet-nam-vs-palestine.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 h\u00f4m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>B\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam lu\u00f4n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup n\u0103m 2008 hay g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U15 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110N\u00c1 2017 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Olympic-Viet-Nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-Bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 7 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Quang H\u1ea3i, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh trung \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho nh\u1eefng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang sang Indonesia 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111i ASIAD b\u1edfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. &ldquo;T\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t cao b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Ch\u01b0a ai l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111i d\u1ef1 Asiad c\u1ea3&rdquo;, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng &lsquo;h\u00edp&rsquo; n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f3 n\u00e9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23+3 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Palestine, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 &ldquo;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38-372-193643.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38-372-193643.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (Gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 cho nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&nbsp;bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng hay nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00ednh Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m thay nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n cho c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m kh\u00e1 r\u00e1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thay v\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,&hellip; th\u1ea7y Park ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/olympicvn230-7-18-1532942727426829334077.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 th\u00f4ng minh, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u1eabn Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng ch\u1eafc, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n xoay x\u1edf t\u1ed1t trong ph\u1ea1m vi h\u1eb9p, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft hay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao Ti\u1ebfn Linh, ngay c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay 3/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y m\u00f9ng 5 v\u00e0 7/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0ng&rsquo; &ndash; c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ecdi vui cho c\u00e1c \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a-168-193636.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a-168-193636.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: Ch\u1edd m\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam-168-193638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam-168-193638.html\">Nh\u00f3m d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1eadp ri\u00eang, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o tay V\u0103n L\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng 3/8, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp ri\u00eang, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong-472-192622.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong-472-192622.html\">Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1954","checkdouble":"193642"},{"date":"15:13 03/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (Gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Palestine gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 3/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 VI\u1ec6T NAM VS U23 PALESTINE</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oB6LYECsdcU\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> \u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, VFF ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Vinaphone \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eed l\u1eeda v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c trong m\u1eaft HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn NHM r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p U23 Palestine. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 38 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 38 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/U23-Viet-Nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 100% quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng NHM, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho ASIAD v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Do \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 nghi\u1ec7m n\u00ean c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01a1n tru khi th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ea1i g\u00ec bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 &lsquo;ch\u1ebft b\u1ecf&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0103n \u00fd, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1ea1c quan nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p U23 Palestine, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; V\u0103n Thanh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\nU23 Palestine: Fahkouri; Alashhab, Farawi, Qatmish, Termanini, Abuwada, Fannoun, El-Kayed, Dabbagh, Yousef, Qymbor.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1953","checkdouble":"193643"},{"date":"17:29 03/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Man City gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Jesus v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/chinh-thuc-man-city-giu-chan-jesus-voi-hop-dong-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man City.</h2><h2>Man City trao cho Jesus h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man City t\u1eeb Palmeiras v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017, Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 24 b\u00e0n sau 53 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Jesus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City trao h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean 40%, ch\u1ea1m m\u1ee9c 112.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Man City gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Jesus v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Man City gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Jesus v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/chinh-thuc-man-city-giu-chan-jesus-voi-hop-dong-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Jesus gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u00f4i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Man City l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi. B\u1edfi v\u00ec khi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Man City c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c C\u0110V h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Man City khen ng\u1ee3i Jesus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Txiki Begiristain c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi khi The Citizens gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Jesus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJesus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. V\u1eady n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Pep Guardiola sung s\u01b0\u1edbng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Jesus th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1952","checkdouble":"193650"},{"date":"16:43 03/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 h\u00f4m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>B\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam lu\u00f4n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup n\u0103m 2008 hay g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U15 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110N\u00c1 2017 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Olympic-Viet-Nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-Bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 7 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Quang H\u1ea3i, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh trung \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho nh\u1eefng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang sang Indonesia 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111i ASIAD b\u1edfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. &ldquo;T\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t cao b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Ch\u01b0a ai l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111i d\u1ef1 Asiad c\u1ea3&rdquo;, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng &lsquo;h\u00edp&rsquo; n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f3 n\u00e9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23+3 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Palestine, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 &ldquo;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38-372-193643.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-38-372-193643.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (Gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 cho nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&nbsp;bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng hay nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00ednh Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m thay nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n cho c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m kh\u00e1 r\u00e1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thay v\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,&hellip; th\u1ea7y Park ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/olympicvn230-7-18-1532942727426829334077.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 th\u00f4ng minh, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u1eabn Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng ch\u1eafc, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n xoay x\u1edf t\u1ed1t trong ph\u1ea1m vi h\u1eb9p, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft hay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao Ti\u1ebfn Linh, ngay c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay 3/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y m\u00f9ng 5 v\u00e0 7/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0ng&rsquo; &ndash; c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ecdi vui cho c\u00e1c \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a-168-193636.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-chau-a-168-193636.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: Ch\u1edd m\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam-168-193638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam-168-193638.html\">Nh\u00f3m d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1eadp ri\u00eang, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o tay V\u0103n L\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng 3/8, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp ri\u00eang, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong-472-192622.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong-472-192622.html\">Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1951","checkdouble":"193651"},{"date":"17:07 03/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1edbt lo v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/21/olympic-viet-nam-co-the-bot-lo-voi-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u23 nhat ban\" title=\"u23 nh\u1eadt b\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/3/29/u23-nhat-ban-10-u23-malaysia-kt-danh-bai-chu-nha-u23-nhat-khoac-vai-u23-viet-nam-lot-vao-vck-u23-chau-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang theo m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m HCV Olympic Tokyo 2020, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o tr\u00ean 21 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 mang t\u1edbi Indonesia m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 tr\u1ebb song kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu. Theo danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong chi\u1ec1u nay 3/8, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG J-League 1. 6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i J-League 2 v\u00e0 n\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i sinh vi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf tr\u1eddi \u00c2u nh\u01b0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tomiyasu Takehiro (thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i B\u1ec9), th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Yamaguchi Takaji (thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha) hay Ritsu Doan (thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan). B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed l\u00e0 \"Messi Nh\u1eadt\" - Takefusa Kubo (17 tu\u1ed5i) - c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Olympic Nepal, Pakistan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong-168-193651.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong-168-193651.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 h\u00f4m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean: Hajime Moriyasu</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">1.\u00a0KOJIMA Ryosuke\u00a0(\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Waseda)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">12. OBI Powell Obinna\u00a0(\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Ryutsu Keizai)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4.\u00a0ITAKURA Kou\u00a0(Vegalta Sendai - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">20.\u00a0TATSUTA Yugo\u00a0(Shimizu S-Pulse - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">7. HARA Teruki (Albirex Niigata - J2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">5. SUGIOKA Daiki (Shonan Bellmare - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3. OKAZAKI Makoto (F.C. Tokyo - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">10. MIYOSHI Koji (Consadole Sapporo - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2\u3000NAGANUMA Yoichi (FC Gifu - J2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">17\u3000KAMIYA Yuta (Ehime FC - J2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">8\u3000MITOMA Kaoru (\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Tsukuba)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">6\u3000HATSUSE Ryo (Gamba Osaka - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">11\u3000ENDO Keita (Yokohama F\u30fbMarinos - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">19\u3000FUNAKI Kakeru(Cerezo Osaka - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">13\u3000IWASAKI Yuto (Kyoto Sanga - J2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">14\u3000MATSUMOTO Taishi (Sanfrecce Hiroshima - J1)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16\u3000WATANABE Kouta (Tokyo Verdy - J2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">18. MAEDA Daizen (Matsumoto Yamaga - J2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">9. HATATE Reo (\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Juntendo)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">15. UEDA Ayase (\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Hosei)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#333333;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1950","checkdouble":"193653"},{"date":"17:28 03/08","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u201cc\u1eebu \u0111en\u201d, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5, khi trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Bianconeri v\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1, trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng AC Milan, \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. C\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juve l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a anh. M\u1ed9t l\u1eddi n\u00f3i th\u1eadt k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5u h\u1eadn CLB \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t Juve l\u1eafm, Bonucci m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ph\u1ea3i u\u1ea5t \u1ee9c l\u1eafm, Bonucci m\u1edbi ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea3nh l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. V\u1eady m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau, anh tr\u01a1 tr\u1ebdn &ldquo;v\u00e1c m\u1eb7t&rdquo; v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 3 ph\u00eda l\u00e0 Juve, Bonucci v\u00e0 Milan. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eb3ng ai nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Bianconeri, hay \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia &ndash; ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gh\u00e9t nhau nh\u01b0 k\u1ebb th\u00f9, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i quay sang v\u00e0 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Bianconeri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Bianconeri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Bonucci-tro-ve-Juventus-Dau-hieu-sup-do-cua-Bianconeri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bonucci t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u01b0\u1eddi trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQuay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017, Juventus khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e3i v\u00e3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5 ra ngay t\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, v\u1edbi Bonucci l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Paulo Dybala &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3, Dani Alves ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 nh\u00e1t ch\u00e2n, khi\u1ebfn Juve \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. HLV Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Dybala, trong khi Bonucci c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Alves ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Bonucci ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Barzagli v\u00ec li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Marcelo qua m\u1eb7t. \u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e3n h\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/he-lo-vu-cai-va-tran-chung-ket-cup-c1-khien-bonucci-dut-tinh-voi-juventus-176-164033.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/15/he-lo-vu-cai-va-tran-chung-ket-cup-c1-khien-bonucci-dut-tinh-voi-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/he-lo-vu-cai-va-tran-chung-ket-cup-c1-khien-bonucci-dut-tinh-voi-juventus-176-164033.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ee5 c\u00e3i v\u00e3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap C1 khi\u1ebfn Bonucci d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i \u0111au kh\u00f3 ngu\u00f4i ngoai, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n g\u00e2y r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 B\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea7m Gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn hai...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, Juve s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn 3 b\u00e0n thua trong hi\u1ec7p 2. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3, 2 k\u1ebb n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n Alves v\u00e0 Bonucci b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do ra \u0111i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Italia th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9 ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Juve, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi tr\u1ecdng d\u00f9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn Milan. <strong>T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng, Allegri \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eaft g\u1ecfng v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Bonucci c\u00e2m mi\u1ec7ng l\u1ea1i, khi anh ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palermo. Ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eeba, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eedi l\u1ea1i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 Allegri n\u00ean c\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>H\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m sau 2 c\u00fa ph\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f3, Bonucci t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng tay Juventus, v\u1edbi l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain va Bonucci co the hoan doi vi tri\" title=\"Higuain v\u00e0 Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Gonzalo-Higuain-dong-y-roi-Juventus-den-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mua Bonucci v\u00e0 chia tay Higuain l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Juve<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 33. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Bonucci, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Cho d\u00f9 g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa 2 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Bianconeri bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi: &ldquo;T\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Bonucci? T\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i trao \u0111\u1ed5i Caldara? T\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n th\u1ea7y&rdquo;?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 Gonzalo Higuain &ndash; c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong 2 m\u00f9a qua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, sang Milan. Nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng Higuain s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ronaldo l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Argentina c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t t\u1edbi c\u00e1ch l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Juve, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dybala Higuain\" title=\"Dybala Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/dybala.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dybala kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ea5t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1ee5c gi\u1eefa, Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i. Tr\u1eeb khi h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam 1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 box-to-box (nh\u01b0 Pogba ho\u1eb7c Savic), b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng Bianconeri s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn b\u1edfi Paulo Dybala kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. T\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e9o l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Juve.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">CR7 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh g\u1ed3ng g\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e3y, trong khi HLV Allegri c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng, Bianconeri v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 x\u01b0ng h\u00f9ng \u1edf Serie A, ch\u1ee9 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c sai l\u1ea7m, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 Higuain ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tan-man/tom-cruise-cristiano-ronaldo-tuoi-tac-co-gi-ma-bat-kha-thi-392-192631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/tom-cruise-cristiano-ronaldo-tuoi-tac-co-gi-ma-bat-kha-thi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tan-man/tom-cruise-cristiano-ronaldo-tuoi-tac-co-gi-ma-bat-kha-thi-392-192631.html\">Tom Cruise - Cristiano Ronaldo: Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus&rdquo; &ndash; Ronaldo l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng trong ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin. Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo-176-192582.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo-176-192582.html\">Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec &ldquo;\u00f4ng gi\u00e0&rdquo; Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u00f4ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c Juventus b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\">Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span><br>\r\nLeonardo Bonucci tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Milan.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1949","checkdouble":"193654"},{"date":"17:47 03/08","title":"Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i thanh l\u00fd sao v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nG\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Anthony Martial l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Franck Ribery l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. Ph\u00eda Man United c\u0169ng nhanh nh\u1ea3u rao b\u00e1n m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Karl-Heinz Rummenigge x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh bao g\u1ed3m: Franck Ribery, Arjen Robben, Kingsley Coman v\u00e0 Serge Gnabry\u201d, Rummenigge n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Bild.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAlphonso Davies c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 cho HLV khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Martial \u201ckh\u00f3 s\u1ed1ng\u201d \u1edf M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, Anthony Martial th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n. Anh r\u1ea5t \u00edt khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng hi\u1ebfm hoi sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho cong khai to thai do khong hai long voi cong tac chuyen nhuong cho Ed Woodward dam nhiem.\" title=\"Jose Mourinho c\u00f4ng khai t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ed Woodward \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Jose-Mourinho-va-Ed-Woodward-Tuan-trang-mat-da-ket-thuc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 22 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y ra b\u00ea b\u1ed1i. Anh xin ph\u00e9p tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3n ng\u01b0\u1eddi con th\u1ee9 2 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng khi qu\u00e1 h\u1ea1n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y quay l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ee9a con b\u00e9 nh\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng sau sinh v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh xin ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Martial tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u01a1n th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Mourinho. Ph\u00eda M.U c\u0169ng ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Monaco v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh c\u00e0ng m\u1edd m\u1ecbt h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina-172-192619.html\">Ch\u00ea Alderweireld v\u00e0 Maguire qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, M.U ch\u1ed1t mua ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\">N\u00f3ng: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-puel-noi-ve-vu-mu-mua-maguire-172-192572.html\">HLV Leicester ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a M.U v\u1ee5 mua Maguire</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-187-192557.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1948","checkdouble":"193655"},{"date":"17:28 03/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-than-trong-khi-nhac-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Pakistan, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/DT-Olympic-Pakistan-than-trong-khi-nhac-toi-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Olympic Pakistan n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Pakistan, \u00f4ng Jose Antonio Nogueira \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng v\u1eady. B\u1ed1n n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhanh. Pakistan kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong ba n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i sinh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pakistan b\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015, do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 can thi\u1ec7p s\u00e2u v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Olympic Pakistan c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Bahrain v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan t\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Olympic Pakistan \u0111ang t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. HLV Antonio Nogueira c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Pakistan s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng\", HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u00f3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0i\u00a0The News.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Pakistan n\u1eb3m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nepal. H\u1ecd m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam ng\u00e0y 14/8, g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hai ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u2018nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng\u2019 nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Pakistan gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-co-the-bot-lo-voi-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-nhat-ban-168-193653.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/21/olympic-viet-nam-co-the-bot-lo-voi-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-co-the-bot-lo-voi-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-nhat-ban-168-193653.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1edbt lo v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong-168-193651.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-giai-tu-hung-quoc-te-bai-test-quan-trong-cho-hang-cong-168-193651.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: B\u00e0i test quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 h\u00f4m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1947","checkdouble":"193656"},{"date":"10:14 03/08","title":"Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB Italia?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-noi-gi-truoc-2-tran-giao-huu-voi-cac-clb-italia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Torino v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m l\u00fd r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKlopp \u0111\u1ec1 cao tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Torino<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi CLB th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Sau \u0111\u00f3, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tham gia chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 2 l\u00fd do. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00ec Liverpool chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Napoli s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Torino v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Torino v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 4 t\u00e2n binh\" title=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/goc-liverpool-qua-roi-thoi-dung-dao-dau-voi-cac-xa-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Torino v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 4 t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Anfield, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi. Alisson, Fabinho, Shaqiri v\u00e0 Naby Keita s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m quen Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 Torino s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p West Ham s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0: &lsquo;\u1ed2, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Anfield&rsquo;.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m quen, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadn k\u1ec1, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed n\u00e1o nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Anfield&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Torino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-liverpool-he-2018-can-them-hai-tan-binh-de-vo-dich-premier-league-172-192590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/Adam-Lallana-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-liverpool-he-2018-can-them-hai-tan-binh-de-vo-dich-premier-league-172-192590.html\">Liverpool c\u1ea7n th\u00eam hai t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Charlie Adam cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam 1-2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/an-dinh-man-ra-mat-cua-bom-tan-ky-luc-liverpool-172-192585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/an-dinh-man-ra-mat-cua-bom-tan-ky-luc-liverpool.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/an-dinh-man-ra-mat-cua-bom-tan-ky-luc-liverpool-172-192585.html\">Klopp \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c Liverpool</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi Liverpool trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Napoli \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Dublin, Ireland ng\u00e0y 4/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1946","checkdouble":"192621"},{"date":"10:18 03/08","title":"Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0110T U16 Iraq b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng tham gia nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tra. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD 2018 (\u1ee6y ban Olympic Indonesia - INASGOC) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Citizen, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a INASGOC x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n b\u1ea3n xin r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban Olympic Iraq. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ASIAD s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i n\u00e0o n\u1eefa. INASGOC v\u00e0 AFC \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c thay \u0111\u1ed5i?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u0169ng b\u00e1c b\u1ecf th\u00f4ng tin Philippines s\u1ebd th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Iraq. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai b\u1ea3ng 5 \u0111\u1ed9i, m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng 3 \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1ea3ng C ASIAD 2018 sau s\u1ef1 r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a Iraq s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Syria v\u00e0 Timor Leste.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Ngo\u00e0i hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u00ec m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng, b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 khi x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 v\u00e0 5 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o &quot;c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng&quot; cho \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, thay v\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ee7i ro theo c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-se-doi-dau-palestine-bang-doi-hinh-nao-168-192601.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-duoc-hua-thuong-tien-ty-cho-tam-hcv-asiad-168-192593.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cac-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192577.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lai-tung-hoa-mu-de-tranh-su-theo-doi-cua-cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-168-192575.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i tung h\u1ecfa m\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018-168-192566.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1945","checkdouble":"192622"},{"date":"10:36 03/08","title":"Arsenal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nwankwo Kanu tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal, n\u1ebfu anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAubameyang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Emirates v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n sau 13 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u2013 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n sang Premier League. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Aubameyang, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Kanu cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Aubameyang r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Aubameyang. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Aubameyang-se-dem-den-danh-hieu-cho-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Arsenal c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal: \u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i cho Emery th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khi b\u1ea1n tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn\u201d \u2013 Kanu k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Lacazette \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\">Arsenal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin Ousmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi-172-192569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi-172-192569.html\">G\u00f3c Arsenal: Ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n5 ch\u1eef k\u00fd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Unai Emery \u0111em v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1944","checkdouble":"192623"},{"date":"10:56 03/08","title":"Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/chelsea-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-ve-tuong-lai-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo Daily Express \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cho Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Tuong-lai-Thibaut-Courtois-da-duoc-Chelsea-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois-180-192010.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mua Courtois </span>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, song Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo Daily Express \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cho Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd do Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 hai l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho Real Madrid. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Chelsea-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-ve-tuong-lai-Courtois-hinh-anh-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua Courtois\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHai m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 Kevin Trapp v\u00e0 Jan Oblak \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Jordan Pickford c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton, Stoke c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1eef Jack Butland b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef Courois.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 hai, Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real Madrid chi ra, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n con s\u1ed1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n hai ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n: Ho\u1eb7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Courtois gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u1eb7c b\u00e1n anh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t xu n\u00e0o t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. Chelsea b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0o ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1943","checkdouble":"192624"},{"date":"11:15 03/08","title":"Bayern Munich ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e1n Jerome Boateng cho MU n\u1ebfu....","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/boateng.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, theo Daily Mail Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U quan t\u00e2m Jerome Boateng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/MU-mua-Jerome-Boateng-thanh-cong-neu-chi-du-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jerome Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Boateng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, Boateng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-boateng-172-192293.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Boateng</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, theo Daily Mail Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h3><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern chi ban Boateng voi gia 50 trieu bang\" title=\"Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/boateng.jpg\"></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, M.U ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ef1u sao Man City, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMirror cho r\u1eb1ng M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Anthony Martial \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u Boateng, song Bayern Munich kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t thay v\u00ec trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Bayern, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Yerry Mina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1942","checkdouble":"192625"}]}